- content_for :title, 'Oasis'

.py-4.border-top.border-medium
  .container
    .row.pt-3
      .col-12.d-md-flex.justify-content-md-between
        %h1.text-danger.pb-3 The Oasis Newsletter
        = render partial: 'shared/oasis_archive_dropdown'
    .row.py-3.mb-3
      .col-md-4
        .card.bg-light
          .card-header
            %h3.h4.my-0.text-danger.text-center May 2021
          .card-body
            = image_tag('card_oasis_2021_05.jpg',
                        alt: 'Oasis Cover - 2021-05',
                        class: 'img-fluid border border-primary')
          .card-footer
            = link_to('Download',
              '/oasis/oasis_2021_05.pdf',
              class: 'btn btn-block btn-outline-danger')
      .col-md-8
        %h2.mb-4.text-danger History of the Oasis
        %p
          The Al Kader "Oasis" began as the newsletter of the temple and was soon a monthly
          publication distributed throughout Al Kader's nobility and the other Shrine Centers of
          the Pacific Northwest.
        %p
          Today, it is also published on the Al Kader website.

